\frac{dy}{dt} = -3a \cdot \cos^2t \cdot \sin t
\frac{dx}{dt} = 3a \cdot \cos t \cdot \sin^2t
\frac{dy}{dx} = \frac{dy}{dt} \cdot \frac{dt}{dx} = \frac{-3a \cdot \cos^2t \cdot \sin t}{3a \cdot \cos t \cdot \sin^2t} = -\frac{\cos t}{\sin t} = -\cot t
